gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 116, Trail Blazers 93
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeated the Trail Blazers, 116-93. Rudy Gobert recorded 24 points (9-11 FG) and 17 rebounds for the Timberwolves, while Karl-Anthony Towns added 23 points, eight rebounds and three 3PM in the victory. Jabari Walker tallied 17 points and 13 rebounds for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Timberwolves improve to 27-11 on the season, while the Trail Blazers fall to 10-28.
